  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPluginController

    public class BatteryActorController
extends AbstractActorController
    Plugin controller for receiving the battery's set power from 4diac-RTE (FORTE). The actor takes an LREAL as the first control signal for the set power and a BOOL for the battery's control mode.
    Author:
    Marc Jakobi

    HTW Berlin

    July 2017
    See Also:
    IForteSocket, CommLayerParams, IPluginController
